{"tid":1933320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科大學生會：習近平新時代具中國特色的社會主義思想冠狀病毒，或稱新冠病毒","createTime":"2020-03-19T08:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T02:37:47.000Z","uid":70301,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ed0e01f9cf01565cc5f62c02d83ad5747ed8f258","tid":1933320,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:26:56.000Z","msg":"《科大學生會就全球抗疫之聲明》<br />\n<br />\n由首宗確診到今下短短幾月間，中國肺炎（習近平新時代具中國特色的社會主義思想冠狀病毒，或稱新冠病毒）肆虐全球，為公共衛生以及各國經濟帶來沉重打擊。我校亦受疫情影響，校內最近亦出現一宗外遊後初步確診個案，患者本月十二日離港，昨日回港時出現病徵並立即送院。患者並非居於科大，校方現正聯絡可能接觸者並提供協助。本會將繼續與校方部門及各宿舍保持聯絡，務求將疫情資訊盡快帶予各位。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於外地疫情嚴峻，本會稍早前通過撥款用以抗疫，部分款項轉予韓國學生會及臺灣學生會，補助當地科大生購買口罩及衛生用品等。本會亦呼籲在外科大學生留意當地衛生部門指示，避免人群及社交活動。仍然身處外地之科大生可參考及分享以下英文字訣保持個人衛生：<br />\n<br />\nW Wash your hands often (經常洗手)<br />\nU Use masks properly and responsibly (正當使用口罩)<br />\nH Have your temperature checked daily (每日量體溫)<br />\nA Avoid large crowds (避免人群)<br />\nN Never touch your face with unwashed hands (未洗手前切忌觸摸面部)<br />\n<br />\n因疫情而中斷學業交流之科大生，可致電校方二十四小時求助熱線+852 3469 2840或聯絡本會尋求協助。本會亦呼籲交流生回港後自行隔離觀察或入住科大臨時隔離中心，避免外出及定期量度體溫。<br />\n<br />\n凡中国製造的，必不持久。本會相信全球合力定能打敗中國肺炎，亦希望世界各國汲取港人經驗，於沙士後停止相信中国政府所謂通報機制，一個打壓示警醫生的政權毫不可信。香港之所以疫情相對輕微，全賴港人在無政府狀態下提早做足準備，坊間及企業等自行籌劃抗疫物資。世界必須謹記中國肺炎發源及擴散之成因，保持警惕，保持戒心，方能避免下一次中国病毒。<br />\n<br />\n科大學生會<br />\n二零二零年三月十八日<br />\n<br />\n#chinese_coronavirus #wuhan_pneumonia #kung_flu_fighting #一命WuFlu #東亞病flu #winnie_the_flu<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/HKUSTSU/photos/a.288100644538118/3313448955336590/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FHKUSTSU%2Fphotos%2Fa.288100644538118%2F3313448955336590%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=1e6ed293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/HKUSTSU/photos/a.288100644538118/3313448955336590/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"d473cc7f44dfb153b7a5d0497afbf4a3e11facb5","tid":1933320,"uid":22707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"師弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c6fbabc34795687e3b3beb0b0e586c64dfe6ea","tid":1933320,"uid":47355,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:32:49.000Z","msg":"winne the flu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2c937b39708662d952a16e11e20a62d45835e2","tid":1933320,"uid":214173,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:37:34.000Z","msg":"你咁講佢又要改過個名架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6410a2767e0862966f29d8b8bf9b965f5f4cf44","tid":1933320,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:53:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200e64925d8ee3b009adf951abb2432ca498e9eb","tid":1933320,"uid":8014,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:57:24.000Z","msg":"仲有以習近平同志為核心的黨中央<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67a3a873aedc94f53886b8bee26450b6e4a8857","tid":1933320,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:58:52.000Z","msg":"識玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755d2e4c07194b5b6b959a75ce229bc0339a996f","tid":1933320,"uid":44309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d192436eacb2faad355ceafb306703116489f32","tid":1933320,"uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2d7ad6b8364f27b38581c3100223a57e999dbe4c","tid":1933320,"uid":306914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e209ca91550f23afbd060eed85bbeea6b7c29172","tid":1933320,"uid":225798,"